{
  "stem": "21582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was all chopped up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And yet, he felt good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So that's where my role models came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when-- when the partisans made themselves more known, the-- the Germans increased their-- their-- their cruelty, their attacks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they-- there were more frequent confrontations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I forgot what you asked me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, at the same time, they-- they saved some-- there was one particular little boy that we saw who was roaming-- who was roaming in the basements, because people were starting to build bunkers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so you-- you could see him roaming underground, and he would disappear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew who he was, but what can you do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We kind of resist, which is we can't kill a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never-- we never-- and-- so there were some people, a few people, and they didn't need many, who apparently communicated to the-- to the Germans where the bunkers were.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I am not sure that every bunker that was broken into, that was-- that was ripped open, was because they knew where they were going, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, what happened was that the Germans intensified their vigilance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They start-- they snuffed out every Jewish life, every partisan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they became even more violent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So for all I know, you know, it was a basement, you just threw a grenade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, I think that they threw-- when they entered our bunker, they threw the grenade in the precise spot where the entrance was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I do remember-- well, then-- then you had these constant attacks, and they try to snuff out all the life, and then we went into the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then-- then our existence was completely subterraneal.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
